{"tid":576891,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺一聽見2019DSE免費就話去考個班人好可悲?","createTime":"2018-03-01T09:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T09:39:36.000Z","uid":35101,"like":9,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c4ec9cf5892355f1674b6c4d033ff3517c8a844a","tid":576891,"uid":35101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"呢度好似有好多連登仔聽見下年免費就話想去考<br />\n一係諗住玩oral撚學生<br />\n一係就諗住oral個陣邀請考官加入討論<br />\n仲有人話大叫MC答案出黎<br />\n<br />\n我唔否認用自修生身份報DSE玩學生/考官真係幾爽<br />\n因為我都諗住玩<br />\n但係點解咁爽既野要免費先去玩呢?<br />\n我真係笑撚咗<br />\n乜連登真係咁多死窮撚? 免費先去考/玩野?<br />\n乜玩一次真係咁貴咩?<br />\n點解唔玩埋今年2018DSE啊?無錢啊? 要政府請你地玩先去玩啊?<br />\n真係好撚可悲<br />\n<br />\n利申: 讀緊 year 1，靠it發咗達，諗住下年開始每年都報dse玩野"},{"pid":"8a4089a75cdd553cb0d82fdb5baf6b88cc119367","tid":576891,"uid":342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a66f169f7adb733354612575a4276336fd8f8b","tid":576891,"uid":33886,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"你想表達啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db32763f676a745953c912204f86e332a4584d8","tid":576891,"uid":11575,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"主旨 : 我發咗達"},{"pid":"eb064fa0e9a478cffef1453486d805adfb77757d","tid":576891,"uid":112627,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"中二病病人"},{"pid":"9e9d1e480524fb5aebbcf6011f7ec8f9dc1e3ec4","tid":576891,"uid":4859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"個問題喺個制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248445a5537d02f5698227599f3e0216e681aba3","tid":576891,"uid":35101,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"14a66f169f7adb733354612575a4276336fd